msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.ellip_func_integrals.ellipeinc:20 of
msgid "Complete elliptic integral of the first kind, near `m` = 1"
msgstr "当 `m` 接近 1 时的第一类完全椭圆积分"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.ellip_func_integrals.ellipeinc:22 of
