#: maxframe.tensor.special.ellip_func_integrals.ellipeinc:41 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.ellip_func_integrals.ellipeinc:42 of
msgid "Wrapper for the Cephes [1]_ routine `ellie`."
msgstr "Cephes [1]_ 例程 `ellie` 的封装。"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.ellip_func_integrals.ellipeinc:44 of
msgid "Computation uses arithmetic-geometric means algorithm."
msgstr "计算使用算术-几何平均算法。"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.ellip_func_integrals.ellipeinc:46 of
msgid ""
"The parameterization in terms of :math:`m` follows that of section 17.2 "
"in [2]_. Other parameterizations in terms of the complementary parameter "
":math:`1 - m`, modular angle :math:`\\sin^2(\\alpha) = m`, or modulus "
":math:`k^2 = m` are also used, so be careful that you choose the correct "
"parameter."
msgstr ""
"参数化方式采用 [2]_ 中第 17.2 节的形式 :math:`m`。其他参数化方式如补参数 "
":math:`1 - m`、模角 :math:`\\sin^2(\\alpha) = m` 或模数 :math:`k^2 = m` "
"也会被使用，因此请确保选择正确的参数。"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.ellip_func_integrals.ellipeinc:52 of
msgid ""
"The Legendre E incomplete integral can be related to combinations of "
"Carlson's symmetric integrals R_D, R_F, and R_G in multiple ways [3]_. "
"For example, with :math:`c = \\csc^2\\phi`,"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.ellip_func_integrals.ellipeinc:56 of
#, fuzzy, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"E(\\phi, m) = R_F(c-1, c-k^2, c)\n"
"  - \\frac{1}{3} k^2 R_D(c-1, c-k^2, c) .\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"E(\\phi, m) = R_F(c-1, c-k^2, c)\n"
"  - \\frac{1}{3} k^2 R_D(c-1, c-k^2, c) 。\n"
"\n"

